Text:
You are about to be presented with a series of images

Please rate how much you like each image.

Please also rate how excited/jittery the image makes you feel (this can be both positive and negative)

instruct_1: How pleasant is the image (1 = very unpleasant; 5 = neutral; 9 = very pleasant)
instruct_2: How excited/jittery does the image make you feel (1 = very bored; 5 = neutral; 9 = very excited)
